OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779048354
OL,3,CScottish police call on Celtic to be
OL,4,C'more accountable' following fan
OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,FScottish police have expressed
OL,8,Ffrustration toward Celtic fans and the
OL,9,Fclub's management following fan
OL,10,Fdisorder in the wake of their match
OL,11,Fagainst Hearts on Saturday.
OL,13,FThere have been 14 arrests in Glasgow
OL,14,Fso far following Celtic's Scottish
OL,15,FPremiership win, which was followed by
OL,16,Fscenes of disorder in parts of the
OL,17,Fcity.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779048354
OL,3,CScottish police call on Celtic to be
OL,4,C'more accountable' following fan
OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,FOf the 14 arrests, 10 were related to
OL,8,FCeltic fans gathering in the Trongate
OL,9,Farea following the match, while four
OL,10,Fwere at the stadium itself.
OL,12,FSome 3,000 supporters congregated in
OL,13,Fthe area on Saturday to celebrate
OL,14,Ftheir team's victory over Hearts.
OL,16,FOfficers had "missiles, including
OL,17,Fglass bottles" thrown at them while
OL,18,Fassisting with a medical emergency,
OL,19,Fpolice said.
OL,26,@xD@NOUyD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779048354
OL,3,CScottish police call on Celtic to be
OL,4,C'more accountable' following fan
OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,FPolice Scotland's Assistant Chief
OL,8,FConstable Mark Sutherland said two
OL,9,Fofficers were injured during disorder
OL,10,Fin the Trongate, while three members
OL,11,Fof the public were either injured or
OL,12,Fsuffered medical episodes.
OL,14,FHe said that so far, there have not
OL,15,Fbeen any arrests in relation to the
OL,16,Fpitch invasion at Celtic Park, but
OL,17,Fwork on the police response to this is
OL,18,Fongoing.
OL,20,FMr Sutherland said: "On this issue,
OL,21,Fmore must be done.
OL,26,@|D@UOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779048354
OL,3,CScottish police call on Celtic to be
OL,4,C'more accountable' following fan
OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,F"Celtic must be more accountable,
OL,8,Fsupported by the local authority with
OL,9,Fpolice, to ensure there are safe
OL,10,Fspaces for people to celebrate, that
OL,11,Fare licensed, controlled.
OL,13,F"And this level of disorder that our
OL,14,Fofficers have faced doesn't happen
OL,15,Fagain."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUwD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779048354
OL,3,CScottish police call on Celtic to be
OL,4,C'more accountable' following fan
OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,FAsked if there is anger from the
OL,8,Fpolice force towards Celtic, he said:
OL,9,F"Absolutely. I have two officers
OL,10,Finjured this morning. I have many more
OL,11,Fofficers who have had rest days
OL,12,Fcancelled.
OL,14,F"Over 400 people had to have their
OL,15,Frest day cancelled."
OL,17,FHe added: "Next year we must have a
OL,18,Fbetter plan and a better contingency,
OL,19,Fso that there's not such a big impact
OL,20,Fon our officers and staff."
OL,26,@qD@AOUvD@AOUwD@TO]yD@KOU|D@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779048354
OL,3,CScottish police call on Celtic to be
OL,4,C'more accountable' following fan
OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,FThe senior officer said he accepted
OL,8,Fthat planning official fan events
OL,9,Fwould be difficult, but stressed he
OL,10,Fdid not think they were impossible.
OL,12,FOf the two injured officers, Mr
OL,13,FSutherland said one had suffered a
OL,14,F"significant" facial injury and the
OL,15,Fother was severely bruised.
OL,17,FHe said that "astonishingly", police
OL,18,Fcame under attack as they were
OL,19,Fresponding to a medical emergency.
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@MO]yD@NOUyD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779048354
OL,3,CScottish police call on Celtic to be
OL,4,C'more accountable' following fan
OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,FThis prompted police to "show a use of
OL,8,Fforce" to end the disturbance.
OL,10,FPolice Scotland are working with
OL,11,FHearts, Mr Sutherland said, and will
OL,12,Ftake "robust and swift action" if any
OL,13,Fcriminality is established.
OL,15,FStreets were awash with green and
OL,16,Fwhite as jubilant fans streamed out of
OL,17,Fthe stadium on Saturday afternoon.
OL,19,FFans were seen climbing on traffic
OL,20,Flights and other objects around the
OL,21,FTrongate.
OL,26,@oD@YOUpD@FO]tD@FOUtD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
