OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779048354
OL,3,CScottish police call on Celtic to be
OL,4,C'more accountable' following fan
OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,FImages on social media showed scuffles
OL,8,Fin the crowd and some clashes with
OL,9,Fpolice.
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FBy around 7.30pm, the streets were
OL,17,Fmostly empty, though large amounts of
OL,18,Frubbish had been left behind.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
