OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779048354
OL,3,CScottish police call on Celtic to be
OL,4,C'more accountable' following fan
OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,FThe disorder came after Police
OL,8,FScotland had earlier accused Celtic of
OL,9,Ffailing to put plans in place for
OL,10,Fofficial Premiership title
OL,11,Fcelebrations.
OL,13,FThe 3`1 victory over the Jambos
OL,14,Fconfirmed the Scottish Premiership
OL,15,Ftitle for Martin O'Neill's Celtic side.
OL,17,FHearts players were escorted off the
OL,18,Fpitch as thousands of Celtic fans
OL,19,Fspilt on to the field following the
OL,20,Ffinal goal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779048354
OL,3,CScottish police call on Celtic to be
OL,4,C'more accountable' following fan
OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,FThe Edinburgh club later released a
OL,8,Fstatement condemning the "shameful"
OL,9,Fscenes, saying: "Reports of serious
OL,10,Fphysical and verbal abuse towards our
OL,11,Fplayers and staff, both on the pitch
OL,12,Fand elsewhere, are deeply disturbing.
OL,14,F"We are investigating this fully and
OL,15,Fare in dialogue with Police Scotland.
OL,17,F"We will make no further comment at
OL,18,Fthis time other than to say that it is
OL,19,Fcompletely unacceptable that our
OL,20,Fplayers and staff were put in that
OL,21,Fsituation."
OL,26,@pD@ZOUpD@cO]qD@QOUvD@AOUyD@AOU}D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
